: 
<bibRefCitation id="9576D6DA2C1CAD83FDF14543F19D12C2" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1748-5967.2011.00352.x" author="Konishi, K" journalOrPublisher="Entomological Research" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" pagination="19 - 27" refId="B13" refString="Konishi, K, Choi, M-B, Lee, J-W, 2012. Review of the East Asian species of the genera Hybrizon Fallen and Ghilaromma Tobias (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Hybrizontinae). Entomological Research 42: 19 - 27" title="Review of the East Asian species of the genera Hybrizon Fallen and Ghilaromma Tobias (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Hybrizontinae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1748-5967.2011.00352.x" volume="42" year="2012">Konishi et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
