<subSubSection id="DB36A5BE158ED3650EEF4FE71BBB5C3B" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="E6242C594792A88508308E6A3E8DF032" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="767ECA5EC3E0C6FCECAB6D5B546AAAD8" pageId="0" pageNumber="11">
Named in commemoration of the much too early deceased hymenopterist Prof. Dr Zai-Fu Xu (South China Agricultural University, Guangzhou; ix.1965 - vi.2017) for his great contributions to our knowledge of the Chinese 
<taxonomicName id="86E1BE8ABD365360346D75D5A27D155A" lsidName="" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="11" rank="order">Hymenoptera</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
